    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">Newport,</name>
                    <date when="1884-08-24">Aug. 24th, '84.</date>
                </dateline>
                <salute>Dear Sir&#8212;</salute>
            </opener>
            <p> I shall go to Boston Tuesday and will endeavor to get a portrait of my
                father&#8212;I have none here.<ptr target="loc.05827_n2"/>
            </p>
            <p> Many thanks for your kind offer of a copy of your book which I gladly accept. </p>
            <closer>
                <salute>Truly yours</salute>
                <signed>Edwin Booth.</signed>
            </closer>
        </body>
    </text>
